metadata.name: ALL IN NFT Podcast First Birthday
metadata.description:
The ALL IN NFT Podcast is celebrating its one-year anniversary, and it's a cause for celebration! 
For the past 12 months, the host of the podcast, Sebastian has been sharing his passion and knowledge about NFTs.

To mark this special occasion, we are immortalizing this 1st of hopefully many more birthdays on the blockchain.

So the one year birthday NFT of the ALL IN NFT podcast is an opportunity to not only celebrate the successes of the podcast, but to look to the growth and development of the NFT industry as a whole into eternity. 

Happy Birthday ALL IN NFT Podcast
